            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價跌近1%　觸及兩周低位",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油價連跌兩日，觸及兩星期低位。美國上星期原油庫存出乎意料增加，加上市場預期OPEC+將會提高產量目標，均拖累油價表現。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報63.48美元，跌49美仙，跌幅0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶66.99美元，跌61美仙，跌幅0.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國能源信息署(EIA)數據顯示，由於煉油廠進入檢修期，美國上星期原油庫存增加240萬桶，增至4.207億桶，市場原先估計減少200萬桶。汽油庫存則在勞動節長周末前減少380萬桶，減幅超出預期。蒸餾油庫存增加170萬桶，有別於估計的減少60萬桶。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15232518-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%911%e3%80%80%e8%a7%b8%e5%8f%8a%e5%85%a9%e5%91%a8%e4%bd%8e%e4%bd%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230704-100638_20230704_fi_source-AP_OilPrice_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 08:45:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指高收350點　標指創新高　數據鞏固減息預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股在非農就業報告公布前夕造好，標普500指數創收市新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">數據鞏固聯儲局減息預期，美國上星期新申領失業救濟人數增至23.7萬人，超出預期，私人市場招聘放緩，顯示就業市場持續降溫。另外，7月貿易逆差擴大近33%至783億美元，引發經濟放緩擔憂。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數收報45621點，升350點，升幅0.77%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數以接近全日高位收市，收報6502點，升53點，升幅0.83%，連升兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數亦兩連升，收報21707點，升209點，升幅0.98%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技及金融股造好，亞馬遜升逾4%，Meta、英特爾、高盛升近2%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">博通高收逾1%，收市後交易時段再升近4%。公司上季每股經調整盈利1.69美元，收入按年升22%至159.5億美元，兩者都超出預期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15232506-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6350%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e6%a8%99%e6%8c%87%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e6%95%b8%e6%93%9a%e9%9e%8f%e5%9b%ba%e6%b8%9b%e6%81%af%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 08:40:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國10年期債息創逾4月新低　聯儲局減息機會增至99%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國10年期及兩年期債息都創逾4個月新低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">10年期債息跌穿4.2厘，低見4.157厘，跌5.4個基點，尾市徘徊4.16厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩年期債息低見3.586厘，跌2.6個基點，尾市回穩至3.59厘附近。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">30年期債息低見4.848厘，跌4.4個基點，創3星期新低，尾市報4.85厘。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">，數據顯示就業市場正在走弱，市場對聯儲局本月稍後重啟減息預期升溫，機率增至99%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15232554-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b10%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%89%b5%e9%80%be4%e6%9c%88%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%8e%e3%80%80%e8%81%af%e5%84%b2%e5%b1%80%e6%b8%9b%e6%81%af%e6%a9%9f%e6%9c%83%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b399",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/static/20230718-default-feature-704x369.jpg",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 08:40:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國海外上月合約銷售按年微跌0.7% 首8月個亦降16.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國海外(00688)公布，今年8月份中國海外系列公司合約物業銷售，為183.3億元(人民幣．下同)，按年微跌0.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國海外\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250722_CR_source_web_haiwai-e1753353100207.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國海外\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250722_CR_source_web_haiwai-e1753353100207.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國海外</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述合約銷售涉及樓面88.85萬平方米，則較去年同期增加27.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首8個月合計，中國海外系列公司累計合約銷售約1503.31億元，按年減少16.5%；涉及樓面666.85萬平方米，按年亦跌0.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至8月底，集團錄得已認購物業銷售約53.63億元，預計將於往後數月內轉化為合約物業銷售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15231487-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c0-7-%e9%a6%968%e6%9c%88%e5%80%8b%e4%ba%a6%e9%99%8d16-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20230720_FI_source-web_00688.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-04 17:35:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中海宏洋上月合約銷售按年增6.1% 首8個月累計仍降10.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國海外宏洋(00081)公布，今年8月份中海宏洋系列公司實現合約銷售21.33億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增加6.1。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_00081-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_00081-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內合約銷售涉及樓面20.32萬平方米，較去年同期也增加4.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首8個月合計，累計合約銷售207.83億元，涉及樓面186.43萬平方米，分別按年下跌10.6%及9.7%。截至8月底，該公司累計認購未簽約額4.39億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15231479-%e4%b8%ad%e6%b5%b7%e5%ae%8f%e6%b4%8b%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e6-1-%e9%a6%968%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e4%bb%8d%e9%99%8d10-6",
